      • loadInBackground

        public List<? extends Parcelable> loadInBackground()
        Description copied from class: AsyncTaskLoaderParcelables
        Called on a worker thread to perform the actual load and to return the result of the load operation. Implementations should not deliver the result directly, but should return them from this method. - Override deliverResult(D) to process results on the UI thread. - Periodically check isLoadInBackgroundCancelled(), and terminate if true. For additional details, see References 1.a.

        loadInBackground in class AsyncTaskLoaderParcelables
